---

<Layout 
  title="Complete Passport Photo Requirements Guide 2025: Sizes, Specs & Free Tools"
  description="Ultimate guide to passport photo requirements for US, India, and 190+ countries. Learn exact dimensions, background rules, and create compliant photos online for free."
>
  <!-- Article Header -->
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-[80px] md:mt-10">
    
    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
